- ## Ethics
#Ethics  #Software #Engineering #AI 
Research in the feld of AI ethics ranges from refections on how ethical principles  can be implemented in decision routines of autonomous machines (Anderson and 101 1 3 The Ethics of AI Ethics: An Evaluation of Guidelines Anderson 2015; Etzioni and Etzioni 2017; Yu et al. 2018) over meta-studies about  AI ethics (Vakkuri and Abrahamsson 2018; Prates et  al. 2018; Boddington 2017;  Greene et al. 2019; Goldsmith and Burton 2017) or the empirical analysis on how  trolley problems are solved (Awad et al. 2018) to refections on specifc problems  (Eckersley 2018) and comprehensive AI guidelines (The IEEE Global Initiative  on Ethics of Autonomous and Intelligent Systems 2019).

- ## Guidelines
#Guidelines #Ethics  #Software #Engineering #AI 
The list of ethics guidelines considered in this article therefore  includes compilations that cover the feld of AI ethics as comprehensively as pos- sible. To the best of my knowledge, a few preprints and papers are currently avail- able, which also deal with the comparison of diferent ethical guidelines (Zeng et al.  2018; Fjeld et al. 2019; Jobin et al. 2019).
